To check Postgresql CRUD you can start node shop.js that wille xecute all te commands of postgresql e-commerce


POSTMAN:
CUSTOMERS
http://localhost:5000/api/customers
PRODUCTS
http://localhost:5000/api/products
ORDERS:
http://localhost:5000/api/orders

/////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////


TO CHECK PURE MONGODB CRUD YOU CAN START NODE mongodbcrud.js that will execute all the cruds of e-commerce 

POSTMAN:
CUSTOMERS
http://localhost:5000/customers/
PRODUCTS
http://localhost:5000/products/
ORDERS:
http://localhost:5000/customers/

/////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////

TO CHECK  MONGODB alongwith mongoose  YOU CAN START NODE mongoosecrud/js that will execute all the cruds of e-commerce 

POSTMAN:
CUSTOMERS
http://localhost:8080/customers
PRODUCTS
http://localhost:8080/products
ORDERS:
http://localhost:8080/orders
